14615931b734079dee97bd49","tid":127100,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面兩張圖係真嘅話  <span style=\"color: red;\">cpu價格應該會大降</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌 啱啱買完7700<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我冇經歷過以前AMD 勁過Intel 年代，所以實際上唔知<br />\n但我覺得Intel 作風唔似會降價<br />\n寧願將高階功能放落去低階U，好似嗰粒2C4T Pentium 但一樣有閹割<br />\n就算真係降，X99 底板價錢都令人卻步<br />\n6800K 唔算係消費級CPU<br />\nIntel 平民版六核照計劃係第9代出<br />\n睇黎冇計劃將X99 降到普及化嘅價錢<br />\n消費級別又冇6核8核產品<br />\n就算降價，消費高階市場今代係咪都要拱手相讓畀AMD<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔明Ryzen 1月就已經發佈，到而加都仲有好多人要去砌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時AMD Ryzen 真係又勁又底用，唔好係到呱呱嘈"},{"pid":"d7d14ba27e03804770bba975728537758ccfa272","tid":127100,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同i7 7700 比，價錢平幾多，效能差幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同性能價錢平你一截<br />\n同價位性能高你一截"},{"pid":"a36cda1294066e2a9c96ad5f182868dc841a2adf","tid":127100,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>效能可能冇咩分別 但分別在於發熱同用電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nryzen冇iGPU所以TDP低d"},{"pid":"ca2e52bb7d22430fd2f3874c7a7f7553e548b0fc","tid":127100,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面兩張圖係真嘅話  cpu價格應該會大降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌 啱啱買完7700<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出面d post重叫人快d出7770k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 3770k 等轉ryzen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f186655b7c42b8d2752031f4576fb1302d66